fc: class Solution { public:     bool canConstruct(string ransomNote, string magazine) {         if (ransomNote.size() > magazine.size()) return false;         vector<int> ht(26);         for (char ch : magazine) {             ht[ch - 'a']++;         }         for (char ch : ransomNote) {             if (--ht[ch - 'a'] < 0) {                 return false;             }         }         return true;     } };

fm: int firstUniqChar(string s) {         vector<int> ht(26);         for (int i = 0; i < s.size(); i++) {             ht[s[i] - 'a']++;         }         for (int i = 0; i < s.size(); i++) {             if (ht[s[i] - 'a'] == 1) {                 return i;             }         }         return -1;     }

fm: int longestPalindrome(string s) {         vector<int> ht(128);         for (char ch : s) {             ht[ch]++;         }         int ans = 0;         for (int i : ht) {             ans += i / 2 * 2;         }         return ans == s.size() ? ans : ans + 1;     }
